{"tid":2161763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[各有各做] 泛民繼續做委任議員 美國照樣制裁議會 有無得諗？","createTime":"2020-08-17T17:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T03:20:26.000Z","uid":331739,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0be414464c09e351a60bfd51ab190fd9248e0e","tid":2161763,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:37:58.000Z","msg":"所謂兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n黃營不分化不指責不內鬥不捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然泛民想繼續做 咁咪繼續做囉 十皮野喎唔知可以幫襯幾多次黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n議會變橡皮圖章 入面班獻世派全部係幫兇 唯一出路就係成個議會制裁佢 邊個喺入面邊個就唔洗再用信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之大家各自做,不內哄不指責, 唔準再屌泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為國際戰線先係主要路線 你集體唔入議會都係為左比美國佬做野姐<br />\n<br />\n佢有佢做花瓶 你有你制裁 係咪最好做法？Super<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144aab3642fdf935f6c85be52a6cb71cd23019e0","tid":2161763,"uid":33868,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"泛民接受委任，美國就會覺得呢班民意代表接受呢個制度"},{"pid":"72e2570858345d1adf5d980c5cac397fc431c914","tid":2161763,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"144aab3642fdf935f6c85be52a6cb71cd23019e0","tid":2161763,"uid":33868,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"泛民接受委任，美國就會覺得呢班民意代表接受呢個制度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人問，成班人quit立法會點樣幫到成件事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c264e68380b0ab81f3d30ebaa462cf1d024105c7","tid":2161763,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"144aab3642fdf935f6c85be52a6cb71cd23019e0","tid":2161763,"uid":33868,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"泛民接受委任，美國就會覺得呢班民意代表接受呢個制度"},"cite